subject: Nascar Nextel Cup Series
Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jeff Gordon, a four-time series champion, heads into the Dickies 500 — the eighth of 10 races in the Chase for the championship — holding a 9-point lead.
